did.abstract:
Part of an eight-part mini-series, this documentary reported by
                        Robert Krulwich tells the stories of married neurosurgeons Isabelle Germano
                        and Joshua Bederson and the challenges of their highly demanding profession;
                        Barry and Renee Gordon and their challenges with their Autistic son Alex;
                        and Howard Lenoff and his relationship with daughter Gloria who suffers from
                        a rare genetic defect Williams Syndrome.
